column2: select top # p.objID, p.ra, p.dec,  p.petroMag_u-extinction_u AS mag_u,  p.petroMag_g-extinction_g AS mag_g, p.petroMag_r-extinction_r AS mag_r, p.petroMag_i-extinction_i AS mag_i, p.petroMag_z-extinction_z AS mag_z, p.petroR5#_r, p.deVRad_r, s.z AS RedShift  from galaxy AS p, dbo.fgetNearByObjEq(#,#,#) AS n, galSpecInfo AS s where p.objid=n.objid and p.specObjID=s.specObjID and p.specObjID<># and s.z># and zWarning = #
